@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = {{JWT_TOKEN}}
@page = 0
@size = 10
@sortBy = createdAt
@sortDirection = DESC

### Transactions: List all for authenticated institution (non-paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transaction-business
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Transactions: Paginated with relations (standard format)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transaction-business/paginated?page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sortBy={{sortBy}}&sortDirection={{sortDirection}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Transactions: Paginated for jQuery DataTable format
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transaction-business/paginated?page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sortBy={{sortBy}}&sortDirection={{sortDirection}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
format: jquery-datatable

draw: 1

### Transactions: Paginated for Ant Design Table format
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transaction-business/paginated?page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sortBy={{sortBy}}&sortDirection={{sortDirection}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
format: ant-table

### Transactions: Paginated with optional filters (institution-scoped)
# Available filters: nis, nama, tahunAkademik, status, invoiceNumber, referenceNumber
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transaction-business/paginated?page={{page}}&size={{size}}&sortBy={{sortBy}}&sortDirection={{sortDirection}}&nis=&nama=&tahunAkademik=&status=&invoiceNumber=&referenceNumber=
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json
